{"tid":331323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解支那人日日講日本人屠殺南京人，但就唔講曾國荃屠殺南京人?","createTime":"2017-07-22T05:40:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-23T02:50:34.000Z","uid":68504,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"caccc3d1576da7c0ae826e8f2b1414757c98e6b1","tid":331323,"uid":68504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T05:40:01.000Z","msg":"點解啲支那人日日講日本人南京大屠殺點樣殘忍，曾國荃殺咁多南京人又唔提?<br />\n<br />\n&quot;湘軍『貪掠奪，頗亂伍。中軍各勇留營者皆去搜括』，&hellip;&hellip;『沿街死屍十之九皆老者。<span style=\"color: red;\">其幼孩未滿二、三歲者亦被戳以為戲</span>，匍匐道上。<span style=\"color: red;\">婦女四十歲以下者一人俱無（均被虜）</span>，老者負傷或十餘刀，數十刀，哀號之聲達於四方。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n&quot;至官軍一面，則潰敗後之虜掠，或戰勝後之焚殺，尤耳不忍聞，目不忍睹，其慘毒實較『賊』又有過之無不及，予不欲言，予亦不敢言也。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n湘軍既行徑同日軍有乜分別? 點解支那人提都唔提? 係咪日本人打輸咗仗好恰啲所以要日日提住? 曾國荃打贏咗，所以支那人就日日拎曾家兄弟打飛機歌功頌德? 真係唔明支那人啲心理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n順便講埋支那食人史，俾大家見識下支那人自古以來啲殘忍嘢<br />\n中國食人史 - 維基百科，自由的百科全書<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E9%A3%9F%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%B2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259B%25BD%25E9%25A3%259F%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258F%25B2&d=2Yu%2B9NqC7gQ3dQGc9WbouKWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=5ff60a0e\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E9%A3%9F%E4%BA%BA%E5%8F%B2</a><br />\n<br />\n易子相食、將&quot;菜人&quot;係街頭拍賣、用人肉人體器官入藥<br />\n乜野花款都有，慢慢欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a822bd6495d823c1a49623210b7b784c7e9d598","tid":331323,"uid":20522,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T05:55:38.000Z","msg":"伯邑考火腿丸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77979b2b09df9cc176e0a26ad91722cc5ae02cbb","tid":331323,"uid":68504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T06:24:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fab2a0efba84ad00ee010e906715198ff988cea8","tid":331323,"uid":55913,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T10:03:33.000Z","msg":"支那狗遲早再被屠殺"},{"pid":"b34e48c4133c5c14a7ac63c0ae71f94996e8b979","tid":331323,"uid":20522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T10:42:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支那狗遲早再被屠殺</blockquote><br />\n成日都發生緊畀支共解放軍屠殺架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5291862ca9711b95399d80f659ad7e2c79205fc","tid":331323,"uid":68504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T12:15:44.000Z","msg":"支那人自古以來都有大量屠殺&ldquo;同胞&rdquo;嘅紀錄，點解仲可以厚住面皮鬧日本人屠殺佢哋？"},{"pid":"807389ecaac56febfa59926727a9ec22cf519ea4","tid":331323,"uid":124991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:01:42.000Z","msg":"東亞嘅戰爭本來就有屠殺嘅傳統，而且呢個傳統都維持咗好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e26940798c81ead5bf8c11ff615e8c17616fecc","tid":331323,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:04:42.000Z","msg":"垃圾民族"},{"pid":"71a9bf76f7a510fc61efb8e391e61ed11dd539c7","tid":331323,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:14:46.000Z","msg":"等睇清朝唔係ChiNa"},{"pid":"bd0ea6208c10f969bc174a4019f9fc8e81a40bf5","tid":331323,"uid":45353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:25:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>支那狗遲早再被屠殺</blockquote><br />\n成日都發生緊畀支共解放軍屠殺架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你睇支那前主席外號叫咩"},{"pid":"1e6a497c8c66f1703391c94062d19ac5d29f3172","tid":331323,"uid":8681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:27:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70058aaae25ee687c2f44de69a92677155738051","tid":331323,"uid":124458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:30:25.000Z","msg":"無知一問 曾國荃定曾國藩？"},{"pid":"0bb6b7fd2db2b6f5cf9aa9193d2fea0f83448c63","tid":331323,"uid":101390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:31:58.000Z","msg":"支那人最叻係內鬥同殺自己人架啦<br />\n仲要覺得好光彩添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a3a033bed8f6cddd2f0b3643bccf118ffa5568","tid":331323,"uid":93266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T14:36:02.000Z","msg":"髒水外潑丫嘛 , 係咁上下啦"},{"pid":"e84c24cada488f99ff49e83561762b83039f3c1d","tid":331323,"uid":68504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T00:16:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無知一問 曾國荃定曾國藩？</blockquote><br />\n屠殺嗰個係曾國荃，但佢大哥曾國藩有份幫佢隱瞞<br />\n<br />\n唔單止屠殺，曾國荃仲係南京搶咗唔少財物入自己袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以話支那人貪污真係有悠久傳統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af8216355b05bdbd3dda4da31018bf979a20d8a5","tid":331323,"uid":5455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T00:21:25.000Z","msg":"Google下長春圍城"},{"pid":"68d6aa9c20c418903911a1b6bea808d26dcb1171","tid":331323,"uid":98163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T00:27:13.000Z","msg":"點解中國人會咁殘暴?係文化定係天生促成?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a361405d77887d3eb9c8407279a7f423835332f","tid":331323,"uid":10064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T00:42:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解中國人會咁殘暴?係文化定係天生促成?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該咁多年內戰入晒dna"},{"pid":"577d87270e0122b953c9be2dd5a97e7df1a722f8","tid":331323,"uid":4180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T01:52:32.000Z","msg":"繼續推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e331be512a6c718428ffaa4aa3e6adbd83d0570","tid":331323,"uid":51546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T02:37:51.000Z","msg":"國際笑話-中華文化"},{"pid":"87c4eaf04ee124c26fb1a6872225b9ba27276d55","tid":331323,"uid":68504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T02:49:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Google下長春圍城</blockquote><br />\n其實長春圍城死嘅人數對支那人嚟講只係小兒科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9545487198fbae030a43ade34e127004076e1f9","tid":331323,"uid":68504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T02:50:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>國際笑話-中華文化</blockquote><br />\n根本就係，唔明啲人有乜好拎嚟打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}